com.salimov.yurii.dao.interfaces

Interface DataDao<T extends Model<E>,E extends java.lang.Number>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Entity type, extends Model.
    E - Entity id type, extends Number.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ArticleDao, CategoryDao, CompanyDao, ContentDao<T,E>, FileDao, MessageDao, ResponseDao, UserDao
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArticleDaoImpl, CategoryDaoImpl, CompanyDaoImpl, DataDaoImpl, FileDaoImpl, MessageDaoImpl, ResponseDaoImpl, UserDaoImpl

    public interface DataDao<T extends Model<E>,E extends java.lang.Number>
    The interface provides a set of standard methods for working models objects of the Model class or subclasses with the database.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Yurii Salimov (yuriy.alex.salimov@gmail.com)
    See Also:
    ArticleDao, CategoryDao, CompanyDao, FileDao, ResponseDao, UserDao, MessageDao, Model
